  * Fixed, (gh#nwg-piotr/nwg-dock-hyprland#49).
  * gotk3 updated.
- Changes from version 0.2.0:
  * Added -lp flag for the launcher button position,
    (gh#nwg-piotr/nwg-dock-hyprland#46).
